        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The guardian is magically bound to an amulet. While the guardian and its amulet are on the same plane of existence, the amulet's wearer can telepathically call the guardian to travel to it, and the guardian knows the distance and direction to the amulet. If the guardian is within 18 m of the amulet's wearer, half of any de dano the wearer takes (round up) is transferred to the guardian.</p>",
          "chat": ""
